<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380834" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/008aGivTgy1gkx4cti3fbj30u01hce83.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="1478" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/008aGivTgy1gkx4cti3fbj30u01hce83.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/008aGivTgy1gkx4cti3fbj30u01hce83-360x520.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/008aGivTgy1gkx4cti3fbj30u01hce83-768x1109.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/008aGivTgy1gkx4cti3fbj30u01hce83-709x1024.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>TechWeb 消息，腾讯欢乐斗地主官方微博发文称，Uzi 成为了官方认证的「欢乐散财童子」。游戏同步上线了 Uzi 定制套装、粉丝系统、Uzi 定制互动表情、场景、牌桌、装扮、语音包等。</p>
