<h4><a href="https://www.benoy.com/zh-hans/%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB/2020/11/designed-by-benoy-alibabas-central-china-headquarters-and-industrial-complex-is-officially-established-in-wuhan/">阿里华中总部设计采用「孔明锁」结构</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380835" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12979_N6_hd.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="563" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12979_N6_hd.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12979_N6_hd-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12979_N6_hd-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>建筑事务所贝诺将负责设计阿里巴巴位于武汉的华中总部暨产业社区基地，预计 2026 年建成。该园区预计占地总面积为 44,654 平米，将融入「阿里立体校园 AliCampus」的概念。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380836" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept.gif" alt="" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept.gif 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Kongming_Lock_concept-360x203.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>作为实现「阿里立体校园」概念的方式，贝诺借用「孔明锁」构成手法，把园区中的「挑战空间」「迭代空间」「韧性空间」「治愈空间」等创新理念空间立体地交错、嵌套和重构，互为支撑。</p>
