<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5301512.html">2020 傅雷翻译出版奖揭晓</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380841" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160596135173065500_a700x398.png" alt="" width="700" height="398" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160596135173065500_a700x398.png 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160596135173065500_a700x398-360x205.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
